Houdini variant builds are available to help studios transition between VFX Platform specifications.  There are Houdini Python 3.10 builds for Linux, macOS and Windows and Houdini gcc 9.3/glibc 2.17 builds for Linux only.  Aside from the deviating Python, gcc and glibc version numbers, the variant builds remain compliant with the rest of the VFX Reference Platform CY2024 specification.
